---
description: Keep object mapping logic centralized in MappingService
alwaysApply: true
---

# Mapping Service Ownership

- All object-to-object mapping must be implemented in `MappingService`.
- Components should not contain inline mapping blocks that shape API/domain data into display models.
- Components may call `MappingService` methods and then handle view flow only (filters, navigation, UI state).
- Add or extend `MappingService` methods when new mapping requirements appear.
- Keep mapping logic reusable and composable; prefer method extraction in `MappingService` over duplicated mapping code across components.
